CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Liminatus Pharma, Inc. is pre-clinical stage biopharmaceutical company developing novel, immune-modulating cancer therapies. The Company's candidate IBA101, is a humanized anti CD47 monoclonal antibody. The next generation CD47 checkpoint inhibitor's initial indication is expected to be patients with advanced solid cancers including non-small cell lung cancer. The Company's vision is to develop a broad array of transformative therapies for cancer patients as a leading global biopharmaceutical company.
